---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Meet the team behind Lead Flow North. We're a woman-owned, proudly Canadian web design and lead generation agency empowering small businesses with modern technology to compete and win."
  structuredData={aboutSchema}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800">
    <!-- Aurora Background Effect -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="aurora-band aurora-band-1"></div>
      <div class="aurora-band aurora-band-2"></div>
      <div class="aurora-band aurora-band-3"></div>
      <div class="aurora-band aurora-band-4"></div>
      <div class="aurora-mouse-glow" id="auroraMouseGlow"></div>
      <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-80 h-80 bg-accent-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            We Help Canadian Small Businesses
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-accent-500">Grow Online</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
            Lead Flow North is a woman-owned, proudly Canadian agency founded on a simple idea: small businesses deserve the same quality digital marketing as big corporations, without the big corporation price tag.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Based in Toronto, we specialize in helping service businesses across Ontario and Alberta generate more leads through high-converting websites and smart automation. Led by CEO Monika Singh and our leadership team, we're on a mission to empower every Canadian small business with enterprise-level technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 mb-1">50%</p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Launch pricing available</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent-500 mb-1">14</p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Day launch guarantee</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4 mt-8">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-600 mb-1">60</p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Days free support</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent-500 mb-1">2026</p>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Year founded</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Our Story
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Three founders. One mission. Make enterprise-level marketing accessible to every Canadian small business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical line (desktop) -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-500/40 via-accent-500/40 to-primary-500/40" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Chapter 1: The Problem -->
        <div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-12 lg:mb-16 items-center">
          <div class="reveal lg:text-right">
