            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Timeline dot -->
          <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 top-8 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary-500 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                <img src="/images/founders/monika.jpeg" alt="Monika Singh, CEO & Co-Founder" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-600 shadow" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Monika Singh</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">CEO & Co-Founder</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm italic border-l-2 border-primary-500/30 pl-4">
                "Small business owners deserved better. They deserved the same technology the big guys use ‚Äî without the big price tag."
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Chapter 2: The Experience -->
        <div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-12 lg:mb-16 items-center">
          <div class="reveal order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                <img src="/images/founders/naveen.jpg" alt="Naveen Gangishetty, COO & Co-Founder" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-600 shadow" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-sm">Naveen Gangishetty</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">COO & Co-Founder</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm italic border-l-2 border-accent-500/30 pl-4">
                "After 15+ years at Dell, Genpact, and consulting across Canada, I learned one thing: the best systems are the ones that actually work for real people."
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Timeline dot -->
          <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 top-8 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-accent-500 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="reveal order-1 lg:order-2">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 bg-accent-50 dark:bg-accent-900/20 rounded-full mb-4">The Experience</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Enterprise skills, small business heart</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Naveen Gangishetty brought 15+ years of enterprise experience ‚Äî from technical support at Genpact, to sales at Dell, to consulting at Service Canada and beyond. Satyadeep built digital solutions for businesses of all sizes as a full-stack developer. They had the tools. They just needed the right mission.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Chapter 3: The Solution -->
        <div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="reveal lg:text-right">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 rounded-full mb-4">The Solution</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Lead Flow North was born</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              In 2026, the three co-founders came together: Monika's vision and leadership, Satyadeep's technical expertise, and Naveen's operational excellence. The goal was simple ‚Äî bring Fortune 500 marketing systems to Main Street businesses at prices that make sense.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- Timeline dot -->
          <div class="hidden lg:flex absolute left-1/2 top-8 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-primary-500 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-900 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-accent-600 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white">
              <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">That's Lead Flow North.</p>
              <p class="text-primary-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                A woman-owned, proudly Canadian company building with early clients. We're not trying to be the biggest agency ‚Äî we're focused on being the best partner for Canadian small businesses who want real results, not just a pretty website that collects dust.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          What We Stand For
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          These aren't just words on a wall. They're the principles we use to make every decision.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {values.map((value) => (
          <div class="reveal bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <span class="text-4xl mb-4 block">{value.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">{value.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">{value.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
